public class RSEdge
extends parlevink.parlegraph.model.MLabeledEdge
implements parlevink.parlegraph.model.MEdge

RSEdge models the edges in a Rhetorical Dependency Structure. It connects a nucleus or a satellite to its RhetRelation. Nuclei and satellites are always RSVertices.
